      "body" : "As reported on IRC (http://bitcoinstats.com/irc/bitcoin-dev/logs/2015/01/14#l1421271863) same issue on my osx 10.10 Retina with `bitcoin-qt-quickfix-e0cd2f55`\r\n\r\n> Build 0.10 against 10.8\r\n\r\nI was always a friend of dropping old os version from the support matrix. 10.8 was released in Feb 2012. 10.7 in Juli 2011.\r\nBut i assume others wish better backward compatibility and dropping 10.7 will probably make people whine about it.",
